HALL
v.

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS NOT ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW French and Stewart, JJ., dissent. Donnelly, J., dissents and would accept the appeal on all propositions of law and hold proposition of law No. III for 2018-1233 and 2018-1479, Moore v. Mt. Carmel Health Sys.
